# CropAbility project context

## What this repo is

GPU-accelerated plant genomics toolkit built on **PyTorch** and **Triton**, with optional **Java** integration via **TorchScript**.

## Layout

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/main/python/cropability/` | Main Python package |
| `src/main/python/pgl/` | Legacy PGL ops and demos |
| `src/main/java/com/example/triton/` | Java TorchScript integration |
| `src/main/torchscript/` | Exported `.pt` models |
| `src/test/python/` | Pytest suite |
| `src/test/java/` | JUnit tests |
| `docs/` | Developer documentation |

## Commands

```bash
pip install -e ".[gpu,dev]"
pytest src/test/python
cropability info
mvn test
```

## Agent guidelines

- Follow `english-only.mdc` for all new docs and comments.
- Prefer changes under `src/main/python/cropability/` for new Python features.
- Do not commit `src/main/resources/private/`.
- Minimize scope: match existing naming and patterns in the file you edit.
- Run relevant tests after substantive code changes.
